NAME
    find_shadows - finds a shadow on an object
 
SYNOPSIS
    #include <acme.h>
    static inherit AcmeShadow;
    #include AcmeShadowInc

    object *find_shadows( object host, string progname );
 
DESCRIPTION
    If you expect someone to have a shadow with a particular 
    program_name, use this to find all instances of it which are
    shadowing that object.
 
EXAMPLE
    find_shadows( THISP, "/usr/zippo/bw/bwshad" ) -> 
      usr/zippo/bw/bwshad#12456
 
SEE_ALSO
    shadow(E), query_shadowing(E), all_shadows(A)
 
LAST MODIFIED                               
    980102
